  "id": "RAW_28fb98b1",
  "title": "别害怕 AI 抢工作，我让两个 AI 帮我打工",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5NDgxOTk1MQ==&mid=2247486118&idx=1&sn=535d8ae2ec56a2b2f36dcb8018f1aa4d",
  "date": "2026-04-09 23:58:00",
  "author": "Playwright实战教程",
  "siteName": "Playwright实战教程",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>欢乐马</span> <span>2026-04-10 07:58</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83fd1b6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FWX3IYB1YgSBGQaryWndicBEV0NM17kgWBYdb0ztXVMKaYVwehA09NlJ339BfiatA25Hq6pWFtMicX8DINqtwpblvoVjowPyZsyPgZgjibQh0ZrE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"960\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001952\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee0164c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FpiaKW2EFGEcXrMu1lVL83v2U8dKFMJ9ykpKGPQHicANwztEgdSCxPQsvTALzyw9pyvjNZUlklI9Pic25mcDvia754w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;padding: 1em;border-left: 4px solid #0F4C81;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);background: #f7f7f7;margin-bottom: 1em;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文为首发知识星球的原创文章《两个AI助手如何直接对话？——小虾×豆包协作实战》的精华版，详细实战与配套源码，已同步至星球。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家好，我是欢乐马。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近AI发展太快，很多人都在焦虑：会不会裁员、会不会被替代、工作还稳不稳。</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">我用一个真实实战告诉你：</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI不是来抢工作的，是来帮你解放双手的。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前每天重复：小虾整理数据 → 我复制 → 豆包写文案 → 我再粘贴回去。昨天一单需求，来回复制粘贴5轮，中间还漏了一条关键信息。我忍无可忍，把它们打通了：</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">让小虾和豆包，直接对话、自己协作、不用我中转。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果超出预期：原本要2小时的沟通，现在</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">几分钟完成</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">；我只需要写一句需求，剩下的交给AI自己搞定。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 0.4em;margin: 1.5em 0;\">\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16.8px;display: table;padding: 0 0.2em;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、我的两个AI助手，到底能干啥？</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;list-style: circle;padding-left: 1em;margin-left: 0;color: #3f3f3f;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">小虾（本地AI）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：擅长本地文件操作、数据整理、API调用，比如</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒级处理10个文件并合并输出</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">\n       <br>\n      </span><span leaf=\"\">这里</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">小虾</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">是我安装的”腾讯龙虾“，有关教程参考：</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5NDgxOTk1MQ==&amp;mid=2247486070&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=36a52598b9c280bc958139e3709f69c7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"腾讯官方&quot;龙虾&quot;来了！QClaw深度体验：微信直连电脑，一句话搞定自动化\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">腾讯官方\"龙虾\"来了！QClaw深度体验：微信直连电脑，一句话搞定自动化</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">豆包（云端AI）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：擅长文案、策略、需求拆解、逻辑输出，比如</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">快速出方案、写文案、做规划</span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话分工：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">小虾管执行与本地，豆包管思考与输出，我只做最终决策。</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 0.4em;margin: 1.5em 0;\">\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16.8px;display: table;padding: 0 0.2em;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、核心方案：API直接对话（稳定不翻车）</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">我没有用</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);font-weight: bold;\">Playwright</span><span leaf=\"\">做网页模拟（验证码多、不稳定），而是用</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">API方案</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;padding-left: 1em;margin-left: 0;color: #3f3f3f;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">1. 我把需求写进 task.md</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">2. 小虾自动读取</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">3. 小虾直接调用豆包API</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">4. 豆包返回结果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">5. 小虾自动保存归档</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">全程</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">不需要我复制粘贴</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，彻底解放。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;border-style: solid;border-width: 2px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);height: 0.4em;margin: 1.5em 0;\">\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16.8px;display: table;padding: 0 0.2em;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">三、真实实战：不是一次成功，是磨了3轮才对齐</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人以为AI对话一次就成，其实</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">真实情况没那么顺利</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><span leaf=\"\">我让它们商量分工：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;list-style: circle;padding-left: 1em;margin-left: 0;color: #3f3f3f;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 第一轮：边界不清，信息对不上</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 第二轮：流程不顺，配合卡顿</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: #3f3f3f;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 第三轮：调整规则、明确角色、统一目录</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #3f3f3f;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: #0F4C81;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">前后磨合3轮，才真正跑通稳定协作。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin: 1.5em 8px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Ya